https://towardsdatascience.com/why-balancing-classes-is-over-hyped-e382a8a410f7
If your imbalanced classes are well separable, have good minority class representation,
and present unique + powerful influences to your outcome variable, then despite being imbalanced,
the data should pose few problems for building solid predictive models